Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:28.59,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Always give my love...  Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:33.80,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Always give my love...  Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:42.03,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Son janai ima kara de mo   Iin janai yareru koto
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.71,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Omotta doori ni yatte miyou   Kimi to deau made
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:59.38,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Nani mo nakatta keredo me o tojite omou
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:04.10,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Issho ni ikiru basho ga aru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:10.60,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Always ai no mune ni yuuki o dashite
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:15.23,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Tatoe sore ga dame da to shite mo ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.61,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Sore dake ga jibun janai
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:26.16,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Kazamuki ga kawatta ima tobitatou
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:31.21,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Always give my love...  Always give my love to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:38.63,RMLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Always give, give my love...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:28.59,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre darei o meu amor... Darei o meu amor para você
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.88,0:21:33.80,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre darei o meu amor... Darei o meu amor para você
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:42.03,TLLyrics12,,0010,0010,0000,,{\fs26}E daí? Nada mais importa. Qual é o problema em fazer o que quisermos?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.12,0:21:52.71,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Vamos fazer o melhor que pudermos, até que o destino nos reúna.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.21,0:21:59.38,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesmo se eu perder tudo, posso fechar meus olhos e ter fé,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.51,0:22:04.10,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,pois existe um lugar onde sempre poderemos nos encontrar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:10.60,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre mantenha a coragem e o amor no seu coração,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.81,0:22:15.23,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Mesmo que você ache que eles são inúteis.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:20.61,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Não! Não sou apenas eu que penso assim...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.74,0:22:26.16,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Sim! Agora que a direção do vento mudou, podemos voar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:31.21,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,Sempre darei o meu amor... Darei o meu amor para você
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.50,0:22:38.63,TLLyrics12,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Sempre te darei o meu amor...
